episodes.title: Neverland Case Files: The Children of Thunder
episodes.description: Welcome back! This is the last cult case of the season and we are coming in with a storm. A prophet, leads a group of others to murder for his greater good. Let’s brace for the storm and dive in.

episodes.title: Neverland Case File: The True Russian Orthodox Church
episodes.description: We are looking into another cult today! This one tried to bury themselves into the side of a mountain to escape doomsday, but their leader didn’t join them? Join me as we open this crazy case!
